HEADWORD: Follicular
<hw>Fol*lic"u*lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Like, pertaining to, or consisting of, a follicles or
follicles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Affecting the follicles; <as>as,
<ex>follicular</ex> pharyngitis</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Folliculated</ent>⟦br⟧
